- Hey.
- Hey.

00:38:16.363 --> 00:38:18.099
- I heard you out here.
- You did?

00:38:18.566 --> 00:38:20.400
- It was a very loud sigh.
- Was it?

00:38:21.235 --> 00:38:22.270
[sighs]

00:38:23.104 --> 00:38:24.404
Can I go first?

