- Depends.
- It's all your fault.

00:38:27.307 --> 00:38:28.943
- No, you can't.
- No, no, no, I mean,

00:38:29.977 --> 00:38:31.311
you're mad at a younger you.

00:38:32.947 --> 00:38:37.919
I'm not like you in a lot of ways, but
I'm way too much like you in others.

00:38:39.419 --> 00:38:41.421
Did you always listen to your mom?

00:38:41.522 --> 00:38:42.790
- I-I mean...
- Of course not.

00:38:44.125 --> 00:38:47.460
Makes me think that the 15-year-old
you would've done exactly what I did,

00:38:47.595 --> 00:38:49.764
- because me and you...
- You and I.

00:38:49.931 --> 00:38:51.431
[sighs]

00:38:51.566 --> 00:38:55.770
You and I aren't wired to just
sit by if we want something.

00:38:56.403 --> 00:38:59.106
I mean, there's this guy that might
be able to tell us about my dad,

00:38:59.273 --> 00:39:00.584
and I was supposed to do nothing?

