I-I need you to keep looking for him.

00:39:36.177 --> 00:39:43.050
So if that means I have to
start listening, then I guess I will.

00:39:43.184 --> 00:39:44.986
- [both chuckling]
- There she is.

00:39:47.188 --> 00:39:48.189
I love you so much.

00:39:48.322 --> 00:39:49.724
I love you too, Mom.

00:39:52.126 --> 00:39:54.362
[sighs] So am I still grounded?

