Can I go to Emma's Halloween party?

00:39:59.033 --> 00:40:01.202
Depends. How
inappropriate is your costume?

00:40:01.335 --> 00:40:04.906
Zombie cheerleader, and
my skirt's longer than yours.

00:40:05.506 --> 00:40:07.842
- That's fair. [Chuckles]
- Can I show you?

00:40:08.009 --> 00:40:11.045
Yes, but I wanna show you
something first. Come here.

00:40:14.715 --> 00:40:17.051
- Is that...
- That's it.

00:40:18.185 --> 00:40:19.220
Have you opened it?

00:40:19.987 --> 00:40:24.191
Yeah. It took me a minute,
but I got there.

00:40:24.992 --> 00:40:27.895
- And?
- I don't know yet.

00:40:28.696 --> 00:40:31.866
I don't know if any of it means
anything or if it's gonna help us find him.

00:40:32.432 --> 00:40:33.500
- Can we?
- Yeah.

